# ---- Rust / Cargo ----

# Compiled artifacts and executables generated by Cargo.
debug/
target/

# Cargo.lock:
#   Commit it for binaries/applications; ignore it for libraries.
#   https://doc.rust-lang.org/cargo/guide/cargo-toml-vs-cargo-lock.html
# Cargo.lock

# Backup files generated by rustfmt.
**/*.rs.bk

# Debug-info files from MSVC builds of rustc (Windows).
*.pdb
#   Exception: Protein Data Bank (.pdb) test fixtures are source files and
#   must be tracked, in any crate (e.g. compute-core/src/md/fixtures/).
!**/fixtures/**/*.pdb
#   Exception: bundled UBL templates compiled in via include_str! are source assets.
!/assets/ubl/*.pdb

# ---- Operating system ----

# macOS: folder attribute metadata.
.DS_Store

# ---- Editors & tools ----

# JetBrains IDEs (IntelliJ, CLion, RustRover, ...).
.idea/

# Visual Studio Code.
.vscode/

# Generic editor backup files (Emacs, Vim, ...).
*~

# Claude Code.
.claude/

# ---- Project-specific ----

# Generated application icon.
/assets/icon/AppIcon.icns
